      "message": "Are you suggesting that we build _all_ plugins on master **just** for Java 21, or that we add *new* pipelines for Java 21 *also*?\n\nI don\u0027t mind working on that, but if this is the only instance for which we need Java 21 plugins, I think we should keep the e2e resolution relative to this plugin by running them on Java 25. It seems much less invasive.\n\nWDYT @luca.milanesio@gmail.com, @david.ostrovsky@gmail.com?",
